rows.label: fev01_110_151_msg0001
rows.name:
This really is so different from sleeping
in that little hut on Gramps's back.

rows.label: fev01_110_151_msg0002
rows.name:
For some reason I even feel like
I've got a bit stronger!

rows.label: fev01_110_151_msg0003
rows.name:
Anyway, better head to
the meet-up point.

rows.label: fev01_110_151_msg0004
rows.name:
It was at Goldmund Exit Dock
down on the ground floor, right?

rows.label: fev01_110_151_msg0005
rows.name:
I guess there's still time to look around
Goldmund a bit longer if I want to...

rows.label: fev01_110_151_msg0006
rows.name: But I shouldn't dawdle too long!
